	<section>
		<title>Overview</title>
			<para>The <classname><html:a target="_parent" href="/library/eregansu/EregansuCore/UUID/">UUID</html:a></classname> class contains facilities for generating and manipulating
Universally Unique Identifiers (UUIDs), according to
<html:a href="http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc4122.txt">RFC 4122</html:a> (equivalent to
ITU-T Rec. X.667, ISO/IEC 9834-8:2005).</para>
			<para><note>Instances of the UUID class are never created; all methods are static.</note></para>
